      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "你是否要鼓我心弦，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "发出你的音乐？"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "是否要使音乐甘甜，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "须有你爱来苦虐？"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "是否当我下倒之时，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "才能识‘爱’的心？"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我是不怕任何损失，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "若你让我来相亲。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "每次的打击，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "都是真利益，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "如果你收去的东西，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "你以自己来代替。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "主，我惭愧，因我感觉"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "总是保留自己，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "虽我也曾受你雕削，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我却感觉受强逼！"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "主，你能否照你喜乐，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "没有顾忌去行，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "不顾我的感觉如何，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "只是要求你欢欣？"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
